extensive shared interests in the current complex and changing 
world situation. 
  To further develop bilateral cooperation of friendship is 
not 
only in the fundamental interest of the two peoples, but also 
beneficial to world peace and development, he said. 
  "I am full of confidence in the further growth of 
Sino-German 
ties," he added. 
  Germany was Qiao's first leg of a three-nation West European 
tour which also takes him to Switzerland and Austria. 

