State Councillor and minister in charge of the State Commission 
for Restructuring the Economy, met with a Romanian Government 
delegation here this morning. 
  The two sides had a cordial talk on topics of common 
interest. 
  The delegation, headed by Mircea Cosea, Romanian minister of 
